# Title Bars
for_window [class="^.*"] border pixel 1
client.focused          #4c7899 #285577 #ffffff #2e9ef4   #285577
client.urgent           #2f343a #900000 #ffffff #900000   #900000

# Gaps
gaps inner 8
gaps outer 3


set $black       #212121
set $darkblack   #000000
set $red         #fb4934
set $darkred     #cc241d
set $green       #b8bb26
set $darkgreen   #98971a
set $yellow      #fabd2f
set $darkyellow  #d79921
set $blue        #83a598
set $darkblue    #458588
